er",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2018-01-30","Prisons: Vocational Guidance","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many careers advisors have been employed in each prison in England and Wales in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Richard Burgon","Leeds East","Richard Burgon","125735"
